# Aura — environment variables
#
# Aura works WITHOUT a key: if ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is unset, every AI feature
# falls back to curated, hand-written responses so the app never errors.
# Add your key below to power the features with live Claude responses.
#
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/  →  copy this file to `.env.local`.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
